      "value": "<p><em><strong>Underdeveloped Hands.</strong></em> Your primitive claws make it hard for you to wield bigger weapons. You can’t use heavy shields. Additionally, you can’t use martial weapons with the two-handed property unless it also has the light property, and if a martial weapon has the versatile property, you can only wield it in two hands.</p>",
